resources.pipeline_activities_note_a: Pipeline activities execute on integration runtime. Pipeline activities include: lookup, get metadata, and schema operations during authoring (test connection, browse folder list and table list, preview data). External pipeline activities are managed on integration runtime but execute on Linked Services. External activities include: Databricks, Stored Procedure, HDInsight activities, and more.
resources.monitoring_note: Monitoring operations include Get and List of Pipeline, Activity, Trigger and Debug Runs.
resources.discount_note: Usage beyond 100 activities/month will receive 20% off their individual cost. Discount will be applied to your bill.
